ABOUT THIS GAME:

Play against computer players each with own betting
aggressiveness, bluffing and tactics. You may choose your
favorite betting structure: Limit, Pot Limit or No Limit. In
Limit Holdem amount that can be bet is set. No Limit Holdem is a
game, where bets are grown very quickly and game tempo is much
faster too. Pot Limit Holdem is a cross between Limit Holdem and
No Limit Holdem.

Version 6.1 adds 10-players table.
